          {
            "clusion": "I",
            "lang": "fr",
            "value": "La population d’étude sera constituée de l’ensemble des personnes vaccinées contre la COVID-19 en France :  - Remplissant le questionnaire initial dans les 2 jours après la première injection du vaccin, - Comprenant la langue française, - Fournissant leur numéro de téléphone ou adresse e-mail, - Donnant leur accord de participation."
          },
          {
            "clusion": "I",
            "lang": "en",
            "value": "To describe ADR incidence rates according to brand of vaccine and to specific populations such as, pregnant women, patients with severe co-morbidities (e.g., frail, vaccinees with auto-immune diseases), elderly, children, patients having recently received other vaccines; - To detect potential novel safety signals; - To identify possible risk factors for ADR."
          },
